= render("static_pages/navigation.html.haml")
.container 
  - flash.each do |key,value|
    %div{:class => 'alert alert-#{key}'}= value  
  .marketing
    %h2{:style=>'text-align: center'} Let's learn more about your personality
    %br
    %center
      <b>If you already know your type (ex. ENTP):</b>
      = form_for :input do |f|
        = text_field :type, 'type'
        %input.button{:name => "commit", :type => "submit", :value => "Enter"}/
    %h4 Otherwise, to get your four character personality "type", we need you to answer the following questions:

    = form_for :input do |f|
      <table border="2" cellpadding="20" align="center">
      <tr><th>Questiion</th><th>Answer</th></tr>
      <tr><td>1. At a party do you:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'EI-1', '1'
      interact with many, including strangers
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'EI-1', '-1'
      interact with a few, known to you
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>2. Are you more:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'SN-1', '1'
      realistic
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'SN-1', '-1'
      philosophically inclined
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>3. Are you more intrigued by</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'SN-2', '1'
      facts
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'SN-2', '-1'
      similes
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>4. Are you usually more:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'TF-1', '1'
      fair minded
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'TF-1', '-1'
      kind hearted
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>5. Do you tend to be more:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'TF-2', '1'
      dispassionate
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'TF-2', '-1'
      sympathetic
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>6. Do you prefer to work:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'JP-1', '1'
      to deadlines
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'JP-1', '-1'
      just "whenever"
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>7. Do you tend to choose:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'JP-2', '1'
      rather carefully
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'JP-2', '-1'
      somewhat impulsively
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>8. At parties do you:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'EI-2', '1'
      stay late, with increasing energy
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'EI-2', '-1'
      leave early, with decreased energy
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>9. Are you more:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'SN-3', '1'
      sensible person
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'SN-3', '-1'
      reflective person
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>10. Are you more drawn to:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'SN-4', '1'
      hard data
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'SN-4', '-1'
      abstruse ideas
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>11. Is it more natural for you to be:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'TF-3', '1'
      fair to others
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'TF-3', '-1'
      nice to others
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>12. In first approaching others are you more:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'TF-4', '1'
      impersonal and detached
      %br
      = f.radio_button 'TF-4', '-1'
      personal and engaging
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td>13. Are you usually more:</td>
      <td>
      = f.radio_button 'JP-3', '1'
